  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the robata grill to medium-high heat",
    "In a bowl, mix together passion fruit pulp, red wine, sugar, and lemon juice",
    "Thread pineapple chunks, kiwi slices, and tofu cubes onto the soaked wooden skewers",
    "Brush the skewers with olive oil and season with salt",
    "Grill the skewers for 8-10 minutes, turning occasionally",
    "Brush the skewers with the passion fruit mixture during the last 2 minutes of grilling",
    "Garnish with chopped fresh mint leaves and serve immediately",
    "Let the skewers rest for a few minutes before serving to allow the flavors to meld together"
